.container-fluid
  .hero-unit
    h1 Trello calendar
    p Show your cards with a due date on a calendar and provide ICS feed.
    p
      a.btn.btn-large.btn-primary(href='/login') Login with Trello

  section.row-fluid
    .span4
      h2 Features
      ul
        li Show cards from your trello boards with a due date
        li Filter cards by boards
        li Show only cards assigned to you
        li Hide archived cards
        li Update due date by drag'n drop
    .span4
      h2 ICS feed
      p
        | The ICS feed allows you to show your cards on Google calendar or Thunderbird Lightning for example.
    .span4
      h2 Security
      p No data are stored on our server.
      p We ask for both read and write permissions. The write permission is to be able to update due date on cards.

  footer
    p This service is not affilied with 
      a(href="https://trello.com") trello
      .
